    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "ATR 72\nLao Airlines\nSAFETY INSTRUCTION CARD\nFOR YOUR SAFETY AND COMFORT PLEASE READ THIS SAFETY INSTRUCTION\nElectronic Devices\nThe following items must not be\nused on board at anytime\nThese items must be turned\noff druring TAKE-OFF\nand LANDING\nSusan Ding TAKE - OFF and LANDING\nFASTEN SEATBELTS\nOXYGEN\nPull Mask\nPut Mask Over\nBreathe Normally\nHelp Others\nNose and Mouth\nFor the passenger who is seated next to an emergency exit. We would like to request your cooperation\nwith us as follow:\n1. Please do not place your belongings at the pass-way of the emergency exit.\n2. Please do not pull the red handle of the emergency exit.\n3. Please read\" Notice of emergency exit in the safety instruction card\" carefully.\n4. You may be asked to open the emergency exit and assist our crew in the event of an emergency.\n5. If you are not available to perform the functions described in the event of an emergency, please ask a flight\nattendant to reseat you."
    ],
